  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink32-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">vāyilvēṇṭip pukuntār kēṭpat talaimakaḷ tōḻikkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink32">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>          amma vāḻi tōḻi makiḻna</l>
<l>          ṉorunā ṇammil vantataṟ keḻunā</l>
<l>          ḷaḻupa veṉpavavaṉ peṇṭir</l>
<l>          tīyuṟu meḻukiṉ ñekiḻvaṉar viraintē.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>          Alas, [my] friend!</l>
<l>          They say his women have been crying for seven days [straight]  –</l>
<l rend='indent2'>          rapidly becoming emaciated like wax melting in fire  –</l>
<l rend='indent2'>          rapidly becoming emaciated like wax melting in fire  –</l>
<l>          [all] because he –  the bringer of joy – came to our house</l> 
  <l rend='indent4'> for [just] one day!</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
